pageContext.claim: “Despite so many false statements and lies, total and complete vindication...and WOW, Comey is a leaker!”
pageContext.analysis: The FBI's investigation into Russian influence on the election continues, so it is not yet a "vindication." Moreover, former FBI James B. Comey leaked one unclassified memo about his conversation with Trump, but Trump himself revealed these conversations existed in his letter firing Comey.
